      "page_number": 1,
      "raw_text": "A meeting of the city council, the\nchamber of commerce and the tax.\npayers league has been called for\ntonight in the council chamber for\nthe purpose of receiving the report\nof the joint committee selected to\nrecommend competent hydraulic\nengineer to assist in preparing the\nplans for giving water protection to\nthe city.\n\n\nThe committee will recommend the\nappointment of e. r. Tannant. son of\nGeneral r. r. Tannant. The engineer\nis a graduate of Washington Agricul-\ntural college. has served in the engi-\nneer corps of the army and has con-\nstructed a large reservoir system.\n\n\nThe plan is to associate b. c. Rib.\nlet with the new engineer and In this\nmanner secure the sservices of boti\nwithout encroaching on the time OF\nMr. Riblet too much"
    }
